Now I have a complete understanding of the codebase. Let me provide a comprehensive implementation plan for the Claymorphism design system integration.

---

# High-Fidelity Claymorphism Design System Implementation Plan

## Executive Summary

This plan outlines the complete transformation of the Badminton Analyzer React application from its current Material Design aesthetic with inline JS styles to a modern Claymorphism design system using Tailwind CSS v4. The project involves 5 pages (Login, Dashboard, Upload, ResultsEnhanced, LivePractice) and requires creating a shared component library while preserving all existing functionality including Supabase auth, i18n, video analysis, and pose detection features.

---

## Phase 1: Foundation Setup (Tailwind CSS v4 + Fonts + Design Tokens)

### Step 1.1: Install Tailwind CSS v4 and Dependencies

**Files to modify:**
- `c:\Users\ASUS\Desktop\Gemini 3 hack\frontend\package.json`

**Commands to run:**
```bash
npm install tailwindcss@next @tailwindcss/vite@next
```

### Step 1.2: Configure Vite for Tailwind v4

**File to modify:**
- `c:\Users\ASUS\Desktop\Gemini 3 hack\frontend\vite.config.js`

**Changes needed:**
```javascript
import { defineConfig } from 'vite'
import react from '@vitejs/plugin-react'
import tailwindcss from '@tailwindcss/vite'

export default defineConfig({
  plugins: [react(), tailwindcss()],
})
```

### Step 1.3: Create Tailwind CSS Configuration with Design Tokens

**New file to create:**
- `c:\Users\ASUS\Desktop\Gemini 3 hack\frontend\src\index.css` (replace existing)

Tailwind v4 uses CSS-based configuration. The file should include:

```css
@import "tailwindcss";

/* ========================================
   CLAYMORPHISM DESIGN TOKENS
   ======================================== */

@theme {
  /* Canvas & Background */
  --color-canvas: #F4F1FA;
  --color-canvas-dark: #E8E4F0;

  /* Text Colors */
  --color-text-primary: #332F3A;
  --color-text-muted: #635F69;
  --color-text-light: #9D99A5;

  /* Accent Colors */
  --color-accent-violet: #7C3AED;
  --color-accent-violet-light: #A78BFA;
  --color-accent-violet-dark: #5B21B6;
  --color-accent-pink: #DB2777;
  --color-accent-pink-light: #F472B6;
  --color-accent-blue: #0EA5E9;
  --color-accent-blue-light: #38BDF8;
  --color-accent-green: #10B981;
  --color-accent-green-light: #34D399;

  /* Status Colors */
  --color-success: #10B981;
  --color-warning: #F59E0B;
  --color-error: #EF4444;
  --color-info: #0EA5E9;

  /* Border Radius (Claymorphism = Super Rounded) */
  --radius-sm: 12px;
  --radius-md: 20px;
  --radius-lg: 28px;
  --radius-xl: 32px;
  --radius-2xl: 40px;
  --radius-full: 9999px;

  /* Font Families */
  --font-display: 'Nunito', system-ui, sans-serif;
  --font-body: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;

  /* Font Weights */
  --font-weight-normal: 400;
  --font-weight-medium: 500;
  --font-weight-semibold: 600;
  --font-weight-bold: 700;
  --font-weight-extrabold: 800;
  --font-weight-black: 900;

  /* Shadow Stacks (4-layer Claymorphism) */
  --shadow-clay-card: 
    0 2px 4px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.04),
    0 4px 8px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.06),
    0 8px 16px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08),
    0 16px 32px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.10);

  --shadow-clay-card-hover: 
    0 4px 8px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.06),
    0 8px 16px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08),
    0 16px 32px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.12),
    0 24px 48px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.14);

  --shadow-clay-button: 
    0 2px 4px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08),
    0 4px 8px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.12),
    0 8px 16px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08),
    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);

  --shadow-clay-pressed: 
    0 1px 2px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.12),
    inset 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);

  --shadow-clay-input: 
    inset 0 2px 4px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.06),
    0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);

  /* Transition Durations */
  --duration-fast: 150ms;
  --duration-normal: 250ms;
  --duration-slow: 400ms;

  /* Animation Easings */
  --ease-bounce: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
  --ease-smooth: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
}

/* Base Layer Resets */
@layer base {
  * {
    @apply font-body;
  }

  html {
    @apply bg-canvas text-text-primary antialiased;
  }

  body {
    @apply min-h-screen;
  }

  h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
    @apply font-display font-bold;
  }
}
```

